Student loan debt has reached $1.747 trillion and 43.4 million borrowers.

@POTUS must cancel student debt because these Americans only wanted an education, and instead they're racking up thousands of dollars in debt.

It's unacceptable.

Student debt has reached $1.749 trillion.

Many of our community members have taken out federal loans to fund their education. They've given back to our community and it's time we give them the freedom from student debt they deserve.

@POTUS can cancel federal student debt today.

